OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FP&O: Government cancels    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcontract over mass sackings
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government has cancelled a contract
OL,6, with P&O Ferries after it sacked nearly
OL,7, 800 staff without notice in March.     
OL,9,FThe Home Office said that a P&O        
OL,10,Fagreement with UK Border Force would   
OL,11,Fcome to an end "with immediate effect".
OL,13,FTransport Secretary Grant Shapps said: 
OL,14,F"We're reforming maritime law to stop  
OL,15,Ffirms exploiting legal loopholes and   
OL,16,Fprotect workers' rights".              
OL,18,FP&O Ferries replaced its sacked staff  
OL,19,Fwith foreign agency workers paid less  
OL,20,Fthan the minimum wage.                 
